title: Native Instruments Velvet Lounge Maschine Expansion [deepstatus]
description:
Native Instruments Velvet Lounge Maschine Expansion [deepstatus]

HEART OF SOUL
Create your own future classics. Melodic kits packed with sampled
Rhodes, vocals, organs, pads, guitar chords, and licks provide the
foundation. MASSIVE patches fill out the low end, while REAKTOR PRISM
adds touches of bells. SFX kits feature processed field recordings,
sampled guitar harmonics, and more. And trap-style programming,
exclusive MASCHINE Drum Synth presets, and 808 beats add the
sophisticated, contemporary edge.

ELEGANT ATMOSPHERE
Future soul is the bridge between the deep musicality of classic soul
and the cutting-edge production of contemporary urban styles.
VELVET LOUNGE draws on elements of the past but with a laser-sharp
focus on experimentation. The result is futuristic music that is
sophisticated, elegant, and progressive.
